          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-sm mb-4">
            <div>
              <span class="text-charcoal/60">Project Type:</span>
              <p class="font-medium">Single-depth basement</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-charcoal/60">Volume:</span>
              <p class="font-medium">45m³</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-charcoal/60">Use:</span>
              <p class="font-medium">Cinema + gym + wine cellar</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-base text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            <strong>Challenge:</strong> Terraced property with neighbours on both sides, one of whom initially objected to Party Wall notice due to previous bad experience with another developer.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed">
            <strong>Solution:</strong> We invited the neighbour to Palace Court, showed photos of our Party Wall monitoring protocols, and offered weekly email updates. Objection withdrawn. Project completed with zero damage to adjacent properties.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-charcoal/10">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3 text-oxidized-copper">Primrose Hill Road (2023)</h3>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-sm mb-4">
            <div>
              <span class="text-charcoal/60">Project Type:</span>
              <p class="font-medium">Double-depth basement</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-charcoal/60">Volume:</span>
              <p class="font-medium">92m³</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-charcoal/60">Use:</span>
              <p class="font-medium">8m lap pool + spa</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-base text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            <strong>Challenge:</strong> Clay soil with high water table. Pool installation required specialized tanking and 24/7 dehumidification system.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed">
            <strong>Solution:</strong> Type C cavity drainage with triple sump pump redundancy. Structural engineer specified deeper piles to counter buoyancy risk from groundwater. Pool commissioned on budget at £1.2M total.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-center text-sm text-charcoal/60 italic mt-8">
        Full case studies with photography will be added once professional project photography is commissioned.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

