          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
            Our affiliation with Hampstead Renovations Group means the construction team reviews basement designs for buildability before you commit. No fantasy drawings.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-oxidized-copper text-cream">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-light mb-6">
        Basement Feasibility Review
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-cream/90 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        Before spending £20-40k on architectural drawings, invest £750 in our Basement Feasibility Review. We assess:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-left text-base text-cream/90 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto space-y-2">
        <li>✓ Soil conditions and groundwater risk</li>
        <li>✓ Party Wall complexity (how many adjoining owners?)</li>
        <li>✓ Planning constraints and approval likelihood</li>
